STATE
v.
Donald G. BARNETTE, Jr. No. 307P14-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Sept. 29, 2015. Donald G. Barnette, Jr., pro se. Rajeev K. Premakumar, Assistant Attorney General, for State of N.C. Brandy Cook, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 3rd of September 2015 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 29th of September 2015."
